    then go ahead, but if you are changing the legal meaning of the text, then you need to create a new version of the section, add
    it here and in the enumeration(call it, for example Section2_v_v2 or something) and then change the logic in the entity to add the
    new section to all new entities.

    The reason is that the accident records must display the legal text that was the law when they were created, and if you just go 
